ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER FOR SECURITY TOOLS:

This firmware includes tools intended for educational and authorized security
testing purposes only. These include, but are not limited to: WiFi deauthentication,
beacon spam, BLE advertisement spoofing, and Bluetooth disruption.

Use of these tools on networks or devices you do not own, or do not have
explicit written permission to test, may violate local, state, and federal
laws in your jurisdiction. In Mexico, unauthorized radio interference and
network disruption are felonies under Article 190 of the Ley Federal de
Telecomunicaciones.

